    "en": {
      "title": "Action announcement on fuel price",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Ministry of Energy said that according to the fuel price formula, there will be no changes in the prices of fuels and the prices of all fuel types will be maintained.",
        "According to the fuel price formula, the fuel prices were to be revised on August 15, but the revisions were not implemented, the official added.",
        "Octane 92 petrol is Rs 450 per litre, Octane 95 petrol is Rs 540 per litre, auto diesel is priced at Rs 430 per liter and super diesel is priced at Rs 510 per litre."
      ],
